imbens.BaseImbalancedEnsemble: An example of how to cooperate imbens with deep learning frameworks like PyTorch. In this example, we first define a simple MLP classifier using PyTorch, and pack  it into a scikit-learn-style wrapper class TorchMLPClassifier. We then use it as  the base estimator of imbens.ensemble.SelfPacedEnsembleClassifier and  train the ensemble on a toy imbalanced dataset.
